{
  "texts": [
    "Edge intelligence facilitates the execution of AI analytics on intelligent edge devices closer to the source.",
    "Recently, pine wilt disease was detected using edge computing (Li et al., 2021).",
    "Likewise, applications like real-time weed mapping and immensely fast image processing have also been reported (Deng et al., 2020; de Camargo et al., 2021; Liu and Wang, 2021).",
    "The arising concept of edge AI, involving the execution of AI models on edge computing devices, is instrumental in reducing the volume of data transmitted to the cloud (Gia et al., 2019).",
    "Notably, Shekhar et al. (2017) proposed a method utilizing a Raspberry Pi equipped with an AI model for automatic irrigation in agricultural fields."
  ]
}